584
00:37:58,240 --> 00:37:58,800
Chi Hu.

585
00:37:58,800 --> 00:37:59,480
At your service.

586
00:37:59,480 --> 00:38:00,640
I leave this to you.

587
00:38:00,840 --> 00:38:02,640
I promised the princess consort

588
00:38:03,480 --> 00:38:06,240
