621
00:40:44,680 --> 00:40:46,960
I can't do it alone.

622
00:40:50,480 --> 00:40:51,960
When you truly need them,

623
00:40:52,080 --> 00:40:52,920
I will

624
00:40:52,920 --> 00:40:54,440
